title: Just 8 months in, India’s vibe-coding startup Emergent claims ARR of over $100M
description: Indian vibe-coding platform Emergent was launched just eight months ago, and it now says it's generating annual recurring revenue of more than $100 million, thanks to surging demand by small businesses and non-technical users.
